name: Eggkick Supreme
description:
THE TIME HAS COME! TO HATCH STRONG AND FERTILE OFFSPRING YOU MUST SLAM YOUR EGG WITH ALL YOUR MIGHT! MAKE IT FLY AS FAR AS POSSIBLE!

Controls are simple, just press SPACE to kick and to restart at the end of a game! Try to get the biggest launch power you can!

Credits:
